**LIX calculator used**: https://www.skolverket.se/skolutveckling/resurser-for-larande/stodmaterial/bedomningsstod-for-larares-vardering-av-elevers-skriftliga-texter/information-om-lix-och-lixer-15

**Word count:** 90
**Number of long words (more than 6 letters):** 71
**Sentence count:** 13
**Average sentence length (in words):** 6.92

**LIX formula:** 
```
LIX = ((antal ord i texten / antal meningar i texten) + (antal l√•nga ord i texten / antal ord i texten)) * 100
```

**LIX calculation:** 
```
LIX = ((90 / 13) + (71 / 90)) * 100
LIX = 6.92 + 0.79 * 100
LIX = 6.92 + 78.69
LIX = 85.61
```

**Result:**
LIX = 85.61